{"tid":1126633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港女陰道運毒偕兩男落網　疑受僱港犯罪集團","createTime":"2019-04-26T13:46:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T18:19:48.000Z","uid":118120,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8c189b057159249bf54785b9ec4ce787aaeb6c7b","tid":1126633,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T13:46:23.000Z","msg":"港女陰道運毒偕兩男落網 疑受僱港犯罪集團 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190426/bkn-20190426144235465-0426_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190426%2Fbkn-20190426144235465-0426_00822_001.html&d=tLsEO8KpRnvfRHW%2FlT3TjreFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=8fcb3466\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190426/bkn-20190426144235465-0426_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190426/photo/bkn-20190426144235465-0426_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190426204737\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190426%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190426144235465-0426_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190426204737&h=8cc3d1c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港女子與兩名澳門男拆家被捕。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190426/photo/bkn-20190426144235465-0426_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190426204737\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190426%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190426144235465-0426_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190426204737&h=d4dd78eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n司警展示行動中檢獲的可卡因及其他證物。 <br />\n<br />\n有香港女子涉嫌以陰道藏毒方式偷運毒品到澳門，再交予兩名澳門男拆家向活躍夜場人士出售。司警周三(24日)晚上於新口岸一間賭場拘捕3人，共檢獲69包可卡因，共重23.6克，市值7.8萬澳門元。 <br />\n<br />\n涉案香港女子姓賴，47歲，報稱侍應，司警在其陰道內發現用避孕套包裹的13袋可卡因。<span style=\"color: red;\">被捕姓何男拆家20歲，在北區某學校就讀初三</span>，另一姓廖男拆家21歲，無業。 <br />\n<br />\n司警根據情報，發現賴到娛樂場寄存行李後，即與2名懷疑拆家接觸，司警遂採取拘捕行動。司警相信他們受僱於香港一個販毒集團，其中賴已販毒個多月，廖和何則販毒兩周。司警落案起訴3人販毒罪，由於賴和廖對相關毒品呈陽性反應，將加控吸毒罪，今日(26日)移送檢察院偵辦。 <br />\n<br />\n20歲讀form 3 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fa195639b01b28c749386c2d9e78106b1107b07","tid":1126633,"uid":51701,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T13:57:04.000Z","msg":"北區某學校<br />\n<br />\n電腦分析一係上官一係鳳溪<br />\n<br />\n兩間學生都係支那人為主"},{"pid":"ff0c29e93d5991ecffd8d6b744353f732b7823cf","tid":1126633,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T13:57:51.000Z","msg":"一定係公屋mk仔"},{"pid":"421c2f081da101b98d4d08a0fe2be960a56ff39b","tid":1126633,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T13:58:35.000Z","msg":"入form3散貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"784ea36f56980c8a942435c377d7fcea62ecac0e","tid":1126633,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:02:56.000Z","msg":"臭閪"},{"pid":"e03af4d5d32f51f714e5254e74363984fca8edd3","tid":1126633,"uid":61882,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"3fa195639b01b28c749386c2d9e78106b1107b07","tid":1126633,"uid":51701,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T13:57:04.000Z","msg":"北區某學校<br />\n<br />\n電腦分析一係上官一係鳳溪<br />\n<br />\n兩間學生都係支那人為主"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:03:24.000Z","msg":"有香港女子涉嫌以陰道藏毒方式偷運毒品到澳門，再交予兩名<span style=\"color: red;\">澳門</span>男拆家向活躍夜場人士出售。<br />\n<br />\n澳門北區呀大偵探<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f1a3db37f2058412acea44454e8fe5d9fb165dd","tid":1126633,"uid":28913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:05:50.000Z","msg":"20歲讀中三<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"834deb8290d7b72a74809012a40d99926fbeaa03","tid":1126633,"uid":5218,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"8c189b057159249bf54785b9ec4ce787aaeb6c7b","tid":1126633,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"