無業。 <br />\n<br />\n司警根據情報，發現賴到娛樂場寄存行李後，即與2名懷疑拆家接觸，司警遂採取拘捕行動。司警相信他們受僱於香港一個販毒集團，其中賴已販毒個多月，廖和何則販毒兩周。司警落案起訴3人販毒罪，由於賴和廖對相關毒品呈陽性反應，將加控吸毒罪，今日(26日)移送檢察院偵辦。 <br />\n<br />\n20歲讀form 3 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:05:51.000Z","msg":"但上面係初三唔係中三喎。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:06:57.000Z","msg":"初中三年級，即係中三<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T15:45:43.000Z","msg":"香港邊有人叫初三，班記者仆街死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33e6705d83948dbe3931ae1c572de5c462bae4d4","tid":1126633,"uid":242872,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T15:48:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a990de7c3249d6c08bd0f17e30b293666e4861f6","tid":1126633,"uid":128210,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"33e6705d83948dbe3931ae1c572de5c462bae4d4","tid":1126633,"uid":242872,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T15:48:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T16:59:04.000Z","msg":"張圖唔係咁用。<br />\n係用係以為自己好出名但其實無人識佢的時候用。<br />\n唔好濫用，ok?"},{"pid":"6f1e77e9ac4410c58b3f6d416d6d3b196f92b44d","tid":1126633,"uid":227275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a990de7c3249d6c08bd0f17e30b293666e4861f6","tid":1126633,"uid":128210,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"33e6705d83948dbe3931ae1c572de5c462bae4d4","tid":1126633,"uid":242872,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T15:48:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T16:59:04.000Z","msg":"張圖唔係咁用。<br />\n係用係以為自己好出名但其實無人識佢的時候用。<br />\n唔好濫用，ok?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T17:14:11.000Z","msg":"哇 你唔講都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b0481a8d2896269673daef86093ca2f818448f","tid":